  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminApproveGrantsServlet
    Servlet for admin to approve grant applications
    AdminDefineGrantCycleServlet
    Servlet to add new grant round
    AdminDeleteGrantCycleServlet
    Servlet to delete grant round
    AdminLoginServlet
    Servlet that uses BCrypt (but not HTTPS) doPost implementation of verifying login credentials
    AdminMarkGrantRoundCompleteServlet
    Servlet that updates grant round as completed
    AdminMarkGrantRoundOpenServlet
    Servlet so admin can mark grant rounds open
    AdminResetServlet
    Servlet to invalidate admin session
    AdminSearchAllSubmissions
    Servlet implementation for admin to search based on specified criteria
    AdminUpdateGrantCycleServlet
    Servlet for admin to update grant round dates
    AdminViewSubmissionsServlet
    Servlet for admin to get all grant request submissions for current grant cycle
    DashboardServlet
    Servlet that forwards to admin dashboard page with appropriate url patterns
    FindDepartmentServlet
    Servlet to find and add departments
    FindTeacherServlet
    Servlet to find and add teacher
    GoToNewSubmissionServlet
    Servlet that forwards user to enter a new submission
    HomeServlet
    Servlet that forwards to main landing page with appropriate url patterns
    ItemServlet
    Servlet that handles part of submission process for adding items
    ResetTeacherDepartment
    Servlet that invalidates session for teacher/department
    Submission1Servlet
    Servlet that finds submissions from current grant cycle for particular teacher or team and processes part 1 of new grant submissions
    Submission2Servlet
    Servlet that processes last part of entries for a new grant submission and sends the object to the dao
    VerifyDepartmentServlet
    Servlet that verifies or updates department info
    VerifyTeacherServlet
    Servlet that verifies or updates teacher info
